Soul_Rend.help: You snap at your target, ripping into their body with nether energy infused jaws. This causes lethal damage and negative energy damage over time.
Soul_Rend.shortHelp: Melee, High DMG(Lethal), Minor DoT (Negative Energy)
Soul_Rend.targetHelp: You are suffering negative energy damage over time.

Maul.help: You slash at your target with your paws. This causes lethal damage and has a chance to knock your target back with the force of the blow.
Maul.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG (Lethal), Chance for Knockback (Foe)

Natures_Fury.help: You rapidly snap at all targets in a cone in front of you, causing lethal damage with each bite to all affected targets.
Natures_Fury.targetHelp: You are suffering lethal damage over time.

Breath_of_the_Nether.help: You unleash a blast of nether energy at your foes, causing negative energy damage and terrorizing them.

Nether_Barrage.help: You unleash a powerful burst of nether energy in a cone before you, causing negative energy damage to all nearby. The intensity of this burst is enough to set opponents ablaze, causing additional fire damage over time.
Nether_Barrage.shortHelp: Ranged (Cone), Moderate DMG (Negative Energy), Minor DoT (Fire)
Nether_Barrage.targetHelp: You are on fire and burning.

Thrill_of_the_Hunt.help: You call upon a pack of Shadow Wolves to assault a single target. These Wolves charge the target, attack it once and then flee.
Thrill_of_the_Hunt.targetHelp: You are under assault by a pack of Shadow Wolves.

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} calls upon a pack of Shadow Wolves to charge you.

Leader_of_the_Pack.help: You inspire yourself and your allies with a powerful howl, increasing damage, run speed and perception.
